Create a LRU cache.

Parameters:
maxEntries - the maximum entries in the cache. Oldest entries will be removed when capacity exceeded.
objectLoader - the callback interface to load object if it can't be found in the cache.
defaultExpirationSec - the expiration for cached objects when loading via objectLoader.
